---
title: Spiced Chicken with Mexican Brown Rice & Bean Medley
description: Lime zest and paprika adds both brightness and smokiness to this weeknight chicken dish. Boneless, skinless thighs stay super juicy, giving this dish extra flavor. We love that everything gets tossed together at the end—it helps all the flavors marry!
